<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA512_04_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_04_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_green" lang="y">윤우는 양갱 12개와 약과 16개를 상자에 남김없이 똑같이 나누어 담으려고 합니다. 양갱과 약과를 상자 몇 개에 나누어 담을 수 있는지 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">양갱 12개와 약과 16개를 똑같이 나누어 담을 수 있는 상자 수에 각각 O표 하세요.</h3>
              <div class="page_1_cont margin_center">
                <div class="boolean_wrap">
                  <h4>상자 수(개)</h4>
                  <button disabled>1</button>
                  <button disabled>2</button>
                  <button disabled>3</button>
                  <button disabled>4</button>
                  <button disabled>5</button>
                  <button disabled>6</button>
                  <button disabled>7</button>
                  <button disabled>8</button>
                  <button disabled>9</button>
                  <button disabled>10</button>
                  <button disabled>11</button>
                  <button disabled>12</button>
                  <button disabled>13</button>
                  <button disabled>14</button>
                  <button disabled>15</button>
                  <button disabled>16</button>
                </div>
                <div class="boolean_wrap">
                  <h4>양갱</h4>
                  <button data-answer-single="true" class="selected"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button class="beforeBgGreen" disabled></button>
                  <button class="beforeBgGreen" disabled></button>
                  <button class="beforeBgGreen" disabled></button>
                  <button class="beforeBgGreen" disabled></button>
                </div>
                <div class="boolean_wrap">
                  <h4>약과</h4>
                  <button data-answer-single="true" class="selected"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false"></button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true"></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">양갱 12개와 약과 16개를 상자 몇 개에 똑같이 나누어 담을 수 있는지 모두 선택해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="flex justify_center">
                <div class="boolean_wrap">
                  <button data-answer-single="true">1</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true">2</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">3</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="true">4</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">5</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">6</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">7</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">8</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">9</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">10</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">11</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">12</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">14</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">15</button>
                  <button data-answer-single="false">16</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">양갱과 약과를 최대한 많은 상자에 똑같이 나누어 담는다면 상자 몇 개에 나누어 담을 수 있는지 알아보세요.</h3>

              <div class="question_box flex justify_center">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span lang="y">개</span>
                </div>
              </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset active" lang="y">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck active" lang="y">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
